_sText:
This is my version of the famouse scoutzknivez map.

Change Log

Added Ropes so that the players can reach areas without the need of sv_gravity 150
Changed the basic theme to wood
Added maxplayers for T: 20 and also for CT
Changed Grass Skin
Fixed Position of the T exit door on the 1st floor
Changed the Floor, Celing, Wall skin of Huts on the 1st Floor and added wooden window sils
Moved the Over hanging slanted grass parts from the top left corner of the map (Screenshot E) backwards so they dont over hang.
Added an extra Pillar to the bridge
Changed one of the pillars for the bridge
Changed the skybox material to militiahdr
Added Fade-in for map start
Changed Ceiling texture for T and CT Bases
Lowered the Ceiling in the T Base
Added supports for the one of the lights in T base (identical to the other room)
Added wooden bridge from the top of T base to the Middle Tower
Changed all metal (except for lights) to wood
Fixed Numerous parts on walls where the grass wasnt slanted
Removed a pointless wall near T base
Changed the block on the cut in part near T base to a Pillar and changed the celing texture there to the same as the CT and T base

And More...
